headline: America's Most Shell-ebrated Job is Back: Bigger, Bolder and Crunchier Than Ever
summary: If you've never been told to "break out of your shell," this is the job for you. With over 20,000 miles driven annually and countless memories made, the PLANTERS速 NUTmobile will once again hit the road in June 2026 and the PLANTERS速 brand is seeking three adventurous Peanutters to go along for the ride.
